      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Skulking Among the Sand",
        "Client": "A-purr-entice Palico",
        "Description": "Heeelp! I went hunting in the\r\nSandy Purr-lains with my\r\nmeowster, but we can\u0027t handle\r\na single monster\u2014much less\r\nTHREE! I hate to say it, but we\r\naren\u0027t up to scratch for this! We\r\nneed a veteran to take the reins!",
